sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant SDK as Kubeflow SDK<br/>Python Client
    participant API as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>Go Operator
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant Master as Master Pod<br/>Rank 0
    participant Workers as Worker Pods<br/>Rank 1-N
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Registry as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 1: TrainJob Submission and Execution

    User->>SDK: Create TrainJob<br/>(framework, workers, runtime)
    SDK->>API: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>Webhook: Validate TrainJob<br/>TLS 1.2+ Webhook cert
    Webhook-->>API: Validation OK
    API-->>SDK: TrainJob Created

    Controller->>API: Watch TrainJob CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create JobSet<br/>TLS 1.2+
    API-->>Controller: JobSet Created

    JobSetCtrl->>API: Create Master Pod
    JobSetCtrl->>API: Create Worker Pods

    Note over Master,Workers: Flow 2: LLM Fine-tuning with DeepSpeed

    Master->>Workers: DeepSpeed Init<br/>23456/TCP (plaintext)

    Master->>HF: Download Base Model<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ Token
    HF-->>Master: Model Artifacts

    Workers->>HF: Download Base Model<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ Token
    HF-->>Workers: Model Artifacts

    Workers->>S3: Fetch Training Data<br/>HTTPS AWS credentials
    S3-->>Workers: Training Dataset

    Note over Master,Workers: Distributed Training in Progress

    loop Training Iterations
        Master->>Workers: Synchronize Gradients<br/>23456/TCP
        Workers-->>Master: Gradient Updates<br/>23456/TCP
    end

    Workers->>S3: Save Checkpoints<br/>HTTPS AWS credentials
    S3-->>Workers: Checkpoint Saved

    Master->>Registry: Register Fine-tuned Model<br/>HTTP Bearer Token
    Registry-->>Master: Model Registered

    Controller->>API: Update TrainJob Status<br/>Completed
    API-->>User: Job Complete Notification

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 3: Gang Scheduling with Volcano

    Controller->>API: Create PodGroup CR<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount

    Note over JobSetCtrl: Volcano Scheduler waits<br/>until all pods are ready

    JobSetCtrl->>API: Bind all pods simultaneously<br/>Gang scheduling

    Master->>Workers: Start training<br/>Synchronized start
